---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Citizen Data is a directory dedicated to showcasing Irish civic technology projects that empower citizens, improve government transparency, and strengthen democratic participation across Ireland."
>
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    {/* Page Header Card */}
    <section class="mb-10">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-irish-stone p-8 md:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-irish-green via-white to-irish-orange"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-irish-charcoal mb-4 tracking-tight">
            About Citizen Data
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Celebrating the people and projects building a more open, transparent, and engaged Ireland.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Mission Cards */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
      {/* Who We Are Card */}
      <article class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-irish-stone p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-irish-green/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-irish-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-irish-charcoal mb-3">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Citizen Data is a directory dedicated to showcasing Irish civic technology projects.
          Our goal is to highlight the tools, platforms, and initiatives that empower citizens,
          improve government transparency, and strengthen democratic participation across Ireland.
        </p>
      </article>

      {/* What We Cover Card */}
      <article class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-irish-stone p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-irish-orange/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-irish-orange-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-irish-charcoal mb-3">What We Cover</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          From public spending trackers to election result monitors, petition platforms to
          geospatial data projects, this site brings together the diverse ecosystem of civic tech
          being built for and by the people of Ireland.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    {/* Values / Why It Matters Card */}
    <section class="mb-10">
      <article class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-irish-stone p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-irish-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-irish-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-irish-charcoal mb-4">Why Civic Tech Matters</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Civic technology bridges the gap between citizens and government. By making data accessible,
              processes transparent, and participation easy, these projects help build trust and accountability
              in public institutions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Ireland has a rich tradition of community organising and democratic engagement. The civic tech
              movement is the natural evolution of that spirit — using modern tools to solve modern challenges
              while staying true to the values of openness and fairness.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    {/* CTA Card */}
    <section>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-irish-green to-irish-green-dark rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Explore the Directory</h2>
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Discover the projects making a difference in Irish civic life. Browse by category,
          status, or simply explore what's out there.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-irish-green font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-irish-cream transition-colors shadow-md"
        >
          View All Projects
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
